================================================================================
DATA SOURCE ATTRIBUTION
================================================================================

The data files in data/ aggregate publicly available information from the
following sources. Original data ownership remains with these sources:

  - Binance: Token listing announcements, prices
  - CoinGecko: Quarterly closing prices, market data
  - CoinMarketCap: Market capitalization data
  - Messari: "State of BNB" Q1-Q3 2025 quarterly reports
  - tokenomist.ai: Tokenomics breakdowns
  - CoinLaw: Industry analysis reports

Users of this dataset are encouraged to cite the original sources where
appropriate. Aggregation, harmonization, and corrections by HoKwang Kim are
licensed under CC BY 4.0 as described above.


